    <title>Hexo NexT 主题配置指南</title>
    <url>/2024/03/21/next-config/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo-NexT-主题配置指南"><a href="#Hexo-NexT-主题配置指南" class="headerlink" title="Hexo NexT 主题配置指南"></a>Hexo NexT 主题配置指南</h1><h2 id="1-主题核心配置"><a href="#1-主题核心配置" class="headerlink" title="1. 主题核心配置"></a>1. 主题核心配置</h2><h3 id="1-1-基础设置"><a href="#1-1-基础设置" class="headerlink" title="1.1 基础设置"></a>1.1 基础设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 主题设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">next</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 主题语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 主题样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">scheme:</span> <span class="string">Gemini</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="1-2-布局设置"><a href="#1-2-布局设置" class="headerlink" title="1.2 布局设置"></a>1.2 布局设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 布局设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">layout:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章页面布局</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 文章目录</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 文章目录深度</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">toc_depth:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 文章目录样式</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">toc_style:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-站点信息配置"><a href="#2-站点信息配置" class="headerlink" title="2. 站点信息配置"></a>2. 站点信息配置</h2><h3 id="2-1-基本信息"><a href="#2-1-基本信息" class="headerlink" title="2.1 基本信息"></a>2.1 基本信息</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 站点信息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">我的博客</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">技术分享与生活记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">这是一个使用</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">和</span> <span class="string">NexT</span> <span class="string">主题搭建的个人博客</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">博客,技术,生活</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Your</span> <span class="string">Name</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">Asia/Shanghai</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-2-菜单设置"><a href="#2-2-菜单设置" class="headerlink" title="2.2 菜单设置"></a>2.2 菜单设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 菜单设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-th</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">schedule:</span> <span class="string">/schedule/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-calendar</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-侧边栏设置"><a href="#3-侧边栏设置" class="headerlink" title="3. 侧边栏设置"></a>3. 侧边栏设置</h2><h3 id="3-1-侧边栏位置"><a href="#3-1-侧边栏位置" class="headerlink" title="3.1 侧边栏位置"></a>3.1 侧边栏位置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 侧边栏设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">sidebar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏位置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">left</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏显示时机</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">display:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">width:</span> <span class="number">300</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-2-侧边栏组件"><a href="#3-2-侧边栏组件" class="headerlink" title="3.2 侧边栏组件"></a>3.2 侧边栏组件</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 侧边栏组件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">sidebar_components:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 个人简介</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">profile:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章目录</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 标签云</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tagcloud:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="4-文章设置"><a href="#4-文章设置" class="headerlink" title="4. 文章设置"></a>4. 文章设置</h2><h3 id="4-1-文章显示"><a href="#4-1-文章显示" class="headerlink" title="4.1 文章显示"></a>4.1 文章显示</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文章设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">post:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章摘要</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">excerpt:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章摘要长度</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">excerpt_length:</span> <span class="number">200</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章目录</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章目录深度</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">toc_depth:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-2-文章元数据"><a href="#4-2-文章元数据" class="headerlink" title="4.2 文章元数据"></a>4.2 文章元数据</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文章元数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_meta:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 发布日期</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 阅读时间</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">reading_time:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="5-评论系统"><a href="#5-评论系统" class="headerlink" title="5. 评论系统"></a>5. 评论系统</h2><h3 id="5-1-评论设置"><a href="#5-1-评论设置" class="headerlink" title="5.1 评论设置"></a>5.1 评论设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 评论系统</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 评论系统类型</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">disqus</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 评论系统短名称</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">shortname:</span> <span class="string">your-disqus-shortname</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 评论系统提供商</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">provider:</span> <span class="string">disqus</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 评论系统语言</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="6-统计与分析"><a href="#6-统计与分析" class="headerlink" title="6. 统计与分析"></a>6. 统计与分析</h2><h3 id="6-1-访问统计"><a href="#6-1-访问统计" class="headerlink" title="6.1 访问统计"></a>6.1 访问统计</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 访问统计</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">analytics:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 百度统计</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">baidu_analytics:</span> <span class="string">your-baidu-analytics-id</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Google Analytics</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">google_analytics:</span> <span class="string">your-google-analytics-id</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="6-2-站点统计"><a href="#6-2-站点统计" class="headerlink" title="6.2 站点统计"></a>6.2 站点统计</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 站点统计</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">site_statistics:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 文章数量</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">posts:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 分类数量</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 标签数量</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 总字数</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_words:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="7-其他设置"><a href="#7-其他设置" class="headerlink" title="7. 其他设置"></a>7. 其他设置</h2><h3 id="7-1-搜索功能"><a href="#7-1-搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="7.1 搜索功能"></a>7.1 搜索功能</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 搜索功能</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 搜索类型</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">local</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 搜索范围</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">scope:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 搜索高亮</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">highlight:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="7-2-代码高亮"><a href="#7-2-代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="7.2 代码高亮"></a>7.2 代码高亮</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 代码高亮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 代码高亮主题</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">tomorrow-night</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 代码高亮行号</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">line_number:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 代码高亮自动换行</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrap:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="8-部署设置"><a href="#8-部署设置" class="headerlink" title="8. 部署设置"></a>8. 部署设置</h2><h3 id="8-1-部署配置"><a href="#8-1-部署配置" class="headerlink" title="8.1 部署配置"></a>8.1 部署配置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 部署类型</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 仓库地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">your-repository-url</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 分支</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="9-注意事项"><a href="#9-注意事项" class="headerlink" title="9. 注意事项"></a>9. 注意事项</h2><ol>
<li>确保所有配置项的值都符合预期格式</li>
<li>修改配置后需要重新生成站点</li>
<li>部分功能可能需要安装额外的插件</li>
<li>建议定期备份配置文件</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="10-常见问题"><a href="#10-常见问题" class="headerlink" title="10. 常见问题"></a>10. 常见问题</h2><ol>
<li><p>主题样式不生效</p>
<ul>
<li>检查主题是否正确安装</li>
<li>检查配置文件格式是否正确</li>
<li>清除缓存后重新生成</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>评论系统不显示</p>
<ul>
<li>检查评论系统配置是否正确</li>
<li>确认评论系统账号是否有效</li>
<li>检查网络连接是否正常</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>搜索功能无结果</p>
<ul>
<li>检查搜索配置是否正确</li>
<li>确认文章是否包含关键词</li>
<li>重新生成搜索索引</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
