    <title>Hexo NexT 主题侧边栏配置：文章概要和目录</title>
    <url>/2024/03/21/sidebar-toc/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="配置文章概要和目录"><a href="#配置文章概要和目录" class="headerlink" title="配置文章概要和目录"></a>配置文章概要和目录</h2><p>在 NexT 主题中，侧边栏可以显示文章概要和目录，这对于阅读长文章特别有帮助。以下是具体的配置方法：</p>
<h3 id="1-配置文章概要（Post-Outline）"><a href="#1-配置文章概要（Post-Outline）" class="headerlink" title="1. 配置文章概要（Post Outline）"></a>1. 配置文章概要（Post Outline）</h3><p>在 <code>_config.next.yml</code> 中找到并修改以下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Table of Contents in the Sidebar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Front-matter variable (nonsupport wrap expand_all).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 自动添加列表序号</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">number:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 如果标题宽度超过侧边栏宽度，是否换行</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrap:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 是否展开所有目录</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">expand_all:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 目录最大深度</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">max_depth:</span> <span class="number">6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-配置侧边栏位置和宽度"><a href="#2-配置侧边栏位置和宽度" class="headerlink" title="2. 配置侧边栏位置和宽度"></a>2. 配置侧边栏位置和宽度</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">sidebar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏位置：left（左侧）| right（右侧）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">right</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏宽度（适用于 Muse | Mist 主题）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">width:</span> <span class="number">300</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏显示条件</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># post    - 默认，在文章页面自动展开</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># always  - 在所有页面自动展开</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># hide    - 点击侧边栏按钮时展开</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># remove  - 完全移除侧边栏</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">display:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏内边距（像素）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">padding:</span> <span class="number">18</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 侧边栏与顶部菜单栏的偏移（仅适用于 Pisces | Gemini 主题）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">offset:</span> <span class="number">12</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-在文章中启用目录"><a href="#3-在文章中启用目录" class="headerlink" title="3. 在文章中启用目录"></a>3. 在文章中启用目录</h3><p>在文章的 Front-matter 中添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">你的文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2024-03-21 11:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-配置目录样式"><a href="#4-配置目录样式" class="headerlink" title="4. 配置目录样式"></a>4. 配置目录样式</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 目录样式设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 自动添加列表序号</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">number:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 如果标题宽度超过侧边栏宽度，是否换行</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrap:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 是否展开所有目录</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">expand_all:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 目录最大深度</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">max_depth:</span> <span class="number">6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="5-配置文章信息显示"><a href="#5-配置文章信息显示" class="headerlink" title="5. 配置文章信息显示"></a>5. 配置文章信息显示</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Post meta display settings</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_meta:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">created_at:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">updated_at:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">another_day:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="使用效果"><a href="#使用效果" class="headerlink" title="使用效果"></a>使用效果</h2><p>配置完成后，你的文章页面将会：</p>
<ol>
<li>在侧边栏显示文章目录</li>
<li>目录会自动根据文章标题生成</li>
<li>可以点击目录直接跳转到对应位置</li>
<li>当前阅读位置的目录项会高亮显示</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><ol>
<li>确保你的文章使用了正确的 Markdown 标题格式（# ## ###）</li>
<li>目录只会显示在文章页面</li>
<li>如果文章没有标题，则不会显示目录</li>
<li>建议保持标题层级的连续性，不要跳级使用</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="常见问题"><a href="#常见问题" class="headerlink" title="常见问题"></a>常见问题</h2><h3 id="目录不显示？"><a href="#目录不显示？" class="headerlink" title="目录不显示？"></a>目录不显示？</h3><p>检查以下几点：</p>
<ol>
<li>确认 <code>_config.next.yml</code> 中的 <code>toc.enable</code> 设置为 <code>true</code></li>
<li>确认文章 Front-matter 中设置了 <code>toc: true</code></li>
<li>确认文章中使用了正确的标题格式</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="目录显示不全？"><a href="#目录显示不全？" class="headerlink" title="目录显示不全？"></a>目录显示不全？</h3><ol>
<li>检查 <code>max_depth</code> 设置是否合适</li>
<li>确认标题层级使用正确</li>
<li>检查标题格式是否规范</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="目录不能点击跳转？"><a href="#目录不能点击跳转？" class="headerlink" title="目录不能点击跳转？"></a>目录不能点击跳转？</h3><ol>
<li>确认主题版本是否最新</li>
<li>检查是否有 JavaScript 错误</li>
<li>尝试清除浏览器缓存</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="进阶配置"><a href="#进阶配置" class="headerlink" title="进阶配置"></a>进阶配置</h2><h3 id="自定义目录样式"><a href="#自定义目录样式" class="headerlink" title="自定义目录样式"></a>自定义目录样式</h3><p>你可以在 <code>source/_data/styles.styl</code> 中添加自定义样式：</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义目录样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.post-toc</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.nav-item</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 目录项样式</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">1.8</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">14px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 当前阅读位置的目录项</span></span><br><span class="line">    &amp;<span class="selector-class">.active</span> &gt; <span class="selector-class">.nav-link</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#fc6423</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="优化目录显示"><a href="#优化目录显示" class="headerlink" title="优化目录显示"></a>优化目录显示</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 滚动时固定侧边栏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">sidebar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">sticky:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 显示目录滚动条</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrap:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>合理配置文章概要和目录可以大大提升博客的阅读体验。建议根据自己的需求和偏好调整这些设置，找到最适合的配置方案。</p>
